So Who Actually Does the Work?

ALB Controller = MANAGER
  ❌ does NOT read HTTP
  ❌ does NOT do path routing
  ❌ does NOT do host routing
  ✅ just creates and manages ALB

AWS ALB = WORKER
  ✅ reads HTTP
  ✅ path routing
  ✅ host routing
  ✅ load balancing

NGINX Controller is Different

NGINX Controller = MANAGER + WORKER
  ✅ reads Ingress YAML
  ✅ configures NGINX pod
  ✅ NGINX itself reads HTTP
  ✅ NGINX itself does path routing
  ✅ NGINX itself does host routing
  ✅ NGINX itself does load balancing

Controller and worker are SAME pod ✅

